{"tid":22034,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[十月新番]魔法少女育成計畫 第十話","createTime":"2016-12-04T08:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T04:50:49.000Z","uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2df26a2ef65e93cbdab3e07bbceaf49a2eba822a","tid":22034,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.buzzbooklet.com/content/3f181923b932e2cb917d7723d263ed06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.buzzbooklet.com%2Fcontent%2F3f181923b932e2cb917d7723d263ed06.jpg&h=fccecacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事簡介 <br />\n<br />\n熱門社交遊戲「魔法少女育成計畫」，為數萬人之中僅一人能成為魔法少女的奇蹟般的遊戲。幸運地獲得魔法，過著充實生活的少女們。然而，就在某一天，她們收到遊戲管理單位傳來「裁掉一半人數過多的魔法少女」的片面通知，於是由十六位魔法少女們所帶來的殘酷激烈、慘無人道的殊死競存比賽，從此拉開序幕&hellip;&hellip;！ <br />\n<br />\nSTAFF <br />\n原　　作：遠藤浅蜊 <br />\n原作插畫：マルイノ <br />\n監　　督：橋本裕之 <br />\n系列構成、腳本：吉岡たかを <br />\n角色設計：愛敬由紀子 <br />\n動畫製作：Lerche <br />\n<br />\n點解咁多新番post冇人閞點同高登鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3115821ae75054c0988bab7eba2b773735a74dbe","tid":22034,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"因為真係冇人肯開"},{"pid":"c114f2b614354b61e3f433222d3be9e729c1a0f7","tid":22034,"uid":4286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"唔記得定真係無講，究竟音樂家個魔法係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7152dcb55b4717736e2b0b1b0ab435e9a1922da6","tid":22034,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"人妻死左有D想棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed3a52dbb88169faf2acee08492150f17ca65b3","tid":22034,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:32:42.000Z","msg":"<bloc